Go to this address for more simple explaination
https://cmake.org/cmake-tutorial/

Difference between include_directories and target_include_directories
is the scope. include_directories involves all including
add_subdirectories while target_include_directories must specify
a scope library

include_directories just specify the address
target include_directories specify the name of library and address
